SPELL E Iron Charge - Physical
Xarofos charge foward in a line, dealing insane amount of damage, they will be ministun for 0.2 but if they are Stun by Iron Blast it
will increase its stun duration and while they are stun, they will lose insane amount of armor, Xarofos will gain insane amount of armor 
while he is Charging and will last for 3 seconds after he is done charging, Each enemys hit will grant him bonus health regeneration
that last 7 seconds. When they get stun by Iron Blast and then by Iron Charge, it will refresh that stun duration, the coldown will
reduce by 0.5 for every auto attack done. He got a 0.7 seconds delay before he Charge and the Charge speed is 160% of his total speed

base damage 20 25 30 35 plus 10% 20% 30% 40% of Strenght
increase damage if stun 20 30 40 50 plus 25% of strenght
armor lost 7 14 21 28 while stun
increase stun duration 0.4 0.6 0.8 1.0
increase armor while in charge 12 20 28 36
health regeneration per enemy hit 0.9 1.8 2.7 3.6
coldown 20 19 18 17
